name: fs.s3a.connection.request.timeout
explanation: The value of this configuration is negative, which is not valid. It should be a positive integer or zero. This might cause timeout issues when making HTTP requests to the AWS service.

name: yarn.timeline-service.timeline-client.number-of-async-entities-to-merge
explanation: The value of this configuration is missing. This might cause issues when merging async entities in the timeline service.

name: dfs.client.failover.connection.retries.on.timeouts
explanation: The value of this configuration is zero, which means no retry attempts will be made on socket timeout when establishing a server connection. This might cause connection issues in case of socket timeout.
